lead_paragraph: Liverpool romped into the Europa League final with a 3-0 win over Villarreal on another magical night at Anfield to tee up a showpiece clash with holders Sevilla who swatted away visitors Shakhtar Donetsk 3-1 on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Liverpool Sink Villarreal to Set Up Sevilla Final
